snippet.title: Space Warlord Organ Trading Simulator - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy, sell, and trade organs in a strange and evolving universe.  Dive into the quivering innards of alien capitalism. This is SPACE WARLORD ORGAN TRADING SIMULATOR: the sci-fi body horror market tycoon game you didn't know you needed.
